creator: PAGEE Dev
descriptionHtml:
What is PAGEE?
PAGEE is a 'mobile sticker printer' that anyone can easily create stickers without using ink.
With PAGEE's specialized papers such as Name sticker, Label sticker and etc, users can simply printout stickers to meet their usage.

PAGEE'S FUNCTION

-Printout Name sticker
-Printout Multi index & expiry dates
-Printout Picktogram sticker
-Printout Photo shoot and Images
-Printout Todo list
-Printout Websurfing
-Printout Banner
-Printout Image slice
-Printout Various template
-Printout Image & text editing

PAGEE's feature
-Easily connect to bluetooth by scanning QR code
-Fast Printout to get the result
-Supports various types of papers
-Supports Smartphone emergency power bank

PAGEE's Special cartridge
-Glass sticker cartridge
-Namesticker cartridge
-Aqua sticker cartridge
-Magic sticker cartridge
-Basic sticker cartridge
-Basic cartridge
descriptionShort: PAGEE's users can simply printout stickers to meet their usage.

title: Pagee

creator: PAGEE Dev
descriptionHtml:
The ZALSON APP connects ZALSON label printers to mobile devices such as smartphones via Bluetooth.
You can quickly and easily edit and print labels and stickers necessary for everyday life.

About ZALSON APP

[Provision of various contents]
: With the provision of sample labels for each situation, you can edit and print easily and quickly.

[Sharing function]
: You can share the content you created with other users.

[Save function]
: You can save the created content and re-output/re-edit it at any time.

[Output history function]
: Printouts with ZALSON label printers are automatically saved and can be reprinted at any time.

[Various fonts and emoticons]
: Provides over 20 different fonts and over 500 emoticons for each situation.
*Fonts and emoticons are continuously updated.

[Enhanced editor features]
: You can edit in more detail with the addition of various functions.
descriptionShort: * PAGEE APP has been newly changed to ZALSON APP. *

- Fix bugs and fix app reliability
- Add New Printer
